OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain pushes
OL,6,Fnorth through the evening then
OL,7,Fbecoming dry for a while overnight.
OL,8,FMore cloud and patchy light rain will
OL,9,Fspread in from the west through the
OL,10,Fearly hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy morning with some
OL,13,Fpatchy light rain. Bright spells and
OL,14,Fthe odd shower through the afternoon
OL,15,Fthen some rain in the evening. Warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FQuite
OL,18,Fcloudy on Saturday and Monday, but
OL,19,Fstaying mainly dry. Rain for a time on
OL,20,FSunday. Staying warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
